   SRILANKA-UNREST (Colombo, Sri Lanka) _ President Chandrika
Kumaratunga's long-awaited peace plan for this war torn nation _
embodied in a new constitution that would have given greater
autonomy to the Hindu Tamil minority in this majority Buddhist
Sinhalese nation _ has foundered. By Celia W. Dugger.
