doesn't mean I escape entirely; I and other owners of brick-,
aluminum- and vinyl-covered houses still need to attend to window
frames. Whether your windows have wood, vinyl or aluminum frames, a
little routine maintenance will help keep them working well.
(Cummings, Dayton Daily News). 26.
