there's been plenty of pain to go around, with emotional debates
and close votes on resolutions affecting homosexuals' full
participation in church life. Among Episcopalians and Presbyterians
as well, this has been the summer of discontent. (Dayton Daily
News). 23. WITH ILLUSTRATION
