<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-08-09 13:59 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6722 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u f BC-ONJOBS-COLUMN-BOS &LR;      08-09 1374
