<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-08-09 15:08 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6802 &Cx1f; taf-z
s k BC-ON-LANGUAGE-$ADV13-NY     08-09 1117
