<P>
   &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   A Boston Globe article about the debate over blood tests for
newborns incorrectly stated that test results for a rare blood
disease in a baby girl in Maine were not reported to the parents.
The test in question was not performed at all because it is not
required in Maine.
