<P>
   DRLAURA-DUEL _ Conservative family-advice givers Dr. Laura and
John Rosemond are locking horns over daycare. Laura says it's
always bad; Rosemond isn't so sure. This points up a difference
that divides even conservative soul-mates: Laura puts the child at
the center of the universe and Rosemond puts the parents there. We
also inquire of parents: What does this dispute say about the value
of parenting experts, whose advice floods the media? (Harris,
Atlanta Journal-Constitution) 30.
