   RELIGION
</P>
<P>
   SIDING _ My house has aluminum siding that's in decent shape, so
I don't have to paint the exterior walls. But that doesn't mean I
escape entirely; I and other owners of brick-, aluminum- and
vinyl-covered houses still need to attend to window frames. Whether
your windows have wood, vinyl or aluminum frames, a little routine
maintenance will help keep them working well. (Cummings, Dayton
Daily News) MOVED
