that it would tax an already overwhelmed foster care system, child
welfare systems across the country have not seen an increase in
cases, according to the early findings of two studies. By Somini
Sengupta.
</P>
<P>
   ILL-MOSQUE (Palos Heights., Ill.) _ After town officials tried
to block the construction of a mosque in this Chicago suburb,
mosque leaders agreed to accept a $200,000 payment to stay out of
town. Then the mayor vetoed the plan, the mosque sued and an uproar
ensued. By Pam Belluck.
</P>
<P>
   (MOVED)
</P>
<P>
   SCI-CONJOINED-TWINS (Undated) _ In a surgical tour de force,
performed with minutes to spare, doctors in Boston separated
conjoined twins who shared a heart. Because of highly unusual
circulatory abnormalities, one of the twins was doomed; the
question was, could the other be saved? Through elaborate planning,
including computer modeling, the doctors found a way to save her
and now, at 14 months, she is living with her family in Paterson,
N.J., and doing well. By Denise Grady. (1600 words)
</P>
<P>
   With graphic.
</P>
