<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-AIMEE-REVIEW-LADN </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
LOVE IS WHERE YOU FIND IT
</HEADLINE>
  (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
(Eds: Fact box below) 
Our rating: 3 1/2 stars 
By DAVID KRONKE 
c.2000 Los Angeles Daily News 
<TEXT>
<P>
   Suggest the idea of a movie about Nazis and lesbians in
