Farberbock and Rona Munro, based on Erica Fischer's book. Produced
by Gunter Rohrbach and Hanno Huth. Released by Zeitgeist Films. &QL; 
-Running time: 2 hours, 5 minutes. &QL; 
-Playing: Laemmle's Town Center 5 in Encino, Laemmle's Colorado in
Pasadena, Laemmle's Music Hall 3 in Beverly Hills. &QL;
</P>
