drink to sip on the way home, or be 65 cents ahead tomorrow. I
decided I needed the change more than the soda. As I pulled out of
the newspaper parking lot, cranked up the AC and headed to the
intersection, I saw her, looking like a frightened rabbit. (Ernest
Murray is managing editor of The Lufkin Daily News) MOVED
