<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-08-09 20:20 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7158 &Cx1f; ttc-z
r e BC-CECIL-DEMENTED-REVIEW     08-09 0579
