the recall involves all size P235/75R15 Firestone radial ATX and
radial ATX II tires produced in North America, and Wilderness AT
tires produced at the company's Decatur, Ill., plant. A Ford
Explorer Sport with the Wilderness AT tires. (Ford/The New York
Times)
